long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e:
A simple extension to export/import cookies. Share online accounts without revealing your password.

Features:

+ Export cookies
+ Import cookies
+ Set password to encrypt your cookies
+ Auto-refresh website when import cookies.

Privacy Policy: https://junookyo.gitbook.io/j2team-cookies/privacy-policy

Website: https://www.junookyo.com/2017/07/j2team-cookies-chrome-extension.html

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/junookyo.vn
